synopsis:
{Virgo}
A rookie female cop, who is brought by his superiors to a safe house to execute a drug suspect, must decide whether to go dirty and move up the ranks or keep clean and die.

{Libra}
During an exorcism, an altar boy must decide whether or not to help a priest kill a pregnant woman who is believed to give birth to the Antichrist.

{Leo}
A controlling fashion designer seeks the help of a strange female necromancer to revive his dead boyfriend.

{Scorpio}
An aging photographer hits the jackpot when he gets ahold of the key to the fulfilment of his worldly desires.
